    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i read somewhere online that it's fine as long as they don't have a flu or anything. i've used it for my older kids before without any issues. if he's just running a slight fever, can't i just give him a small dose to get him through the night? i really don't want to wake up the doctor at this hour.",
